<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Activate Your MealApp Account</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #5E4B3A;
                background-color: #F9F5F0;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 20px 0;
            }
            .email-container {
                max-width: 500px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
            .content-box {
                background-color: #FFFFFF;
                border-radius: 8px;
                overflow: hidden;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(94, 75, 58, 0.08);
            }
            .header {
                background-color: #F1E8D9;
                padding: 30px 0;
                text-align: center;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #E0D5C3;
            }
            .logo {
                height: 40px;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }
            h1 {
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: 300;
                color: #5E4B3A;
                letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 40px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .centered-content {
                max-width: 380px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
            .activation-code {
                font-size: 32px;
                letter-spacing: 5px;
                color: #D4A373;
                margin: 30px 0;
                font-weight: 300;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                background-color: #F9F5F0;
                border-radius: 4px;
                display: inline-block;
            }
            .divider {
                height: 1px;
                width: 100%;
                background-color: #F1E8D9;
                margin: 30px auto;
                max-width: 300px;
            }
            .button {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 14px 28px;
                background-color: #D4A373;
                color: white !important;
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 4px;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 20px 0;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
            }
            .button:hover {
                background-color: #C19260;
            }
            .footer {
                padding: 25px;
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 12px;
                color: #A89B8C;
                background-color: #F9F5F0;
            }
            .illustration {
                width: 120px;
                margin: 0 auto 25px;
                display: block;
            }
            p {
                margin: 18px 0;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #5E4B3A;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="email-container">
            <div class="content-box">
                <div class="header">
                    <img src="https://i.imgur.com/JqYeZZn.png" alt="MealApp" class="logo">
                    <h1>Hello <%= name %>! Let's help you reset your password</h1>
                </div>
                
                <div class="content">
                    <div class="centered-content">
                        <svg class="illustration" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="#F1E8D9"/>
                            <path d="M30,65 Q50,80 70,65 L60,40 Q50,30 40,40 Z" fill="#D4A373"/>
                            <circle cx="40" cy="45" r="3" fill="#5E4B3A"/>
                            <circle cx="60" cy="45" r="3" fill="#5E4B3A"/>
                            <path d="M40,55 Q50,60 60,55" stroke="#5E4B3A" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
                        </svg>
                        
                        <p>Welcome to the Spicy community! We're excited to help you discover delicious meals and mealplans from restaurants in your city.</p>
                        
                        <p>To reset your password, please use this verification code:</p>
                        
                        <div class="activation-code"><%= otp %></div>
                        
                        <p>This code will expire in 24 hours.</p>
                        
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        
                        <p>Alternatively, you can click the button below:</p>
                        
                        <a href="https://mealapp.com/activate?token=abc123" class="button">Activate My Account</a>
                        
                        <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="footer">
                    <p>Â© 2025 Spicy. All rights reserved.</p>
                    <p>123 Foodie Street, Culinary City</p>
                    <p>
                        <a href="#" style="color: #A89B8C; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 5px;">Help Center</a> | 
                        <a href="#" style="color: #A89B8C; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 5px;">Privacy</a> | 
                        <a href="#" style="color: #A89B8C; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 5px;">Unsubscribe</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>